MANAGEMENT AUTHORITY

Coastal Dev Management LLC, as General Partner, has exclusive authority to:
(a) manage all day-to-day operations of the Partnership;
(b) execute contracts and agreements binding on the Partnership;
(c) acquire and dispose of Partnership assets;
(d) vote and exercise all rights with respect to interests in entities held by the Partnership.

Limited partners have no management authority. David Jae-Won Park, as sole member of the General Partner entity, ultimately controls all management decisions of the Partnership.
